	<h2>
			EnCrisp to Deliver Cloud Governance Risk and Security Management Solution on the Force.com Platform		</h2>








<div class="news_first">
	<h4>
		<span class="yellow_hover" style="font-size:16px;">New suite of governance products from EnCrisp delivers technology for managing social and corporate GRC in the cloud driven economy.</span></h4>
	<h4>
		<span class="yellow_hover" style="font-size:14px;">Reston, VA (PRWEB) August 29, 2011</span></h4>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:15px;font-family:verdana;">EnCrisp LLC,a leading independent provider of governance, risk and compliance (GRC) solutions, today announced ConfidentG&reg; Enterprise and Social Governance Service built and delivered natively on Force.com, the leading enterprise cloud computing platform. The suite of products include the patent-pending cloud Governance-as-a-Service&trade; platform named ConfidentG&reg;. These sustainable governance, risk and security compliance applications are designed to effectively govern and provide transparency and monitoring across compliance with quality and security standards, industry regulations, risk programs and corporate policies for private and public global organizations of all sizes.</span></p>
	<div align="center">
		<hr align="center" noshade="noshade" size="5" width="415" />
	</div>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:verdana;">These are &ldquo;purpose built&rdquo; cloud GRC solutions that focus not just on internal governance but focus on the collaboration driven by social GRC, leveraging real-time dynamic risk based information from social media channels like Twitter, Facebook and geo-spatial information from Google. The ConfidentG&reg; platform is a GRC platform that leverages the CSA GRC stack across all GRC and security functions, including compliance management, vendor risk management, threat and vulnerability management and overall enterprise risk management.</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:verdana;">With prebuilt cloud governance best practices and partnerships with Cloud Security Alliance (CSA) and over two dozen industry vertical driven governance business solutions, ConfidentG&reg; provides an impactful tool to assess against industry established best practices, ethical and environmental standards and critical compliance requirements.</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:verdana;">&ldquo;Cloud computing is revolutionizing how we execute and implement IT, said Bhavesh C. Bhagat, co-founder of EnCrisp and CEO of Confident Governance. &ldquo;While the need for governance is universal, applications and execution differ by each industry and organization type as well as unique regulatory needs. Confident Governance&#39;s unique Cloud Governance&trade; Rules Studio delivers thousands of industry vertical driven business rules and also enables real-time risk adjustments based on social GRC in which EnCrisp is a pioneer.&ldquo;</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:verdana;">Built on Force.com, the EnCrisp applications include the following features at no cost to end users:&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;No hardware to buy, no software to install, pay as you go.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;No installation required - just login using your browser.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Built by business end-users for businesses. Easy drag and drop UI as well as dashboards for C-level&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Enhance existing GRC lifecycles by enabling extended real-time transparency and monitoring of social media and geo-spatial location based information.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Instantly connect global teams with governance best practices and assessments using powerful governance chatter.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Powerful multi-lingual support - supports over 14 languages, with the ability to add more.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Easy integration to all major enterprise ERP and GRC solutions including Microsoft, Oracle, SAP and other third-party solutions.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Low cost per user, per month (yearly) licensing model saves you money, time and resources.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Scalable: roll out to thousands of users, worldwide simply and quickly.&nbsp;<br />
		&bull;Extend and support a growing eco-system of communication and collaboration technologies, including mobile access on Android devices and iPad.</span></p>
	<p>
		<span class="yellow_hover" style="font-size:16px;">About EnCrisp</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:verdana;">EnCrisp&reg; is an INC 500 award recipient, global leader in Sustainable and Resilient Governance Risk Compliance (GRC) for Cloud Computing technologies and legacy ERP technologies. EnCrisp&rsquo; s Confident Governance product platform is the only global Cloud Governance platform focused entirely on managing and making Cloud Computing secure and well governed. As the only firm specializing in both niche GRC and Cloud Computing governance, EnCrisp excels in designing leading-edge solutions with a &quot;business-driven&quot; risk based approach to improve IT lifecycle, regulatory governance, environmental sustainability, security architecture. With its ConfidentG&reg; business rules platform and GRCWeaverTM industry vertical driven control automation content, EnCrisp delivers a powerful combination of thousands of best practice GRC automation rules and content for different industry verticals, system horizontals and government agencies. EnCrisp is recognized as a salesforce.com ISV partner, Microsoft BizSparks start-up member and specialized SAP GRC and Security Solutions provider globally.</span></p>
	<p>
		<span class="yellow_hover" style="font-size:16px;">About Confident Governance&reg;&nbsp;</span></p>
	<p>
		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:verdana;">Confident Governance&reg; is the first &ldquo;native&rdquo; purpose built Enterprise Cloud Governance Company. Its industry leading products make Governance and Risk Management powerful and affordable for organizations of all sizes enabling organizations to not only focus on governance from within but also from universal external shifts in risks using Social Media and Geo-spatial location based information. Using our applications on our Governance as a Service&trade; platform you can infuse transparency and trust amongst your executives and stakeholders without technical complexity and without having to worry about buying hardware and software. Every aspect of Confident Governance products is designed to make it easier for businesses to implement an Effective Governance, Risk and Security Compliance system to provide clear transparency with easiest non-technical operation enabling truly &quot;Confident Governance&reg;&quot;.</span></p>
	<h4>
		<span class="yellow_hover" style="font-size:16px;">About the Force.com Platform and AppExchange&nbsp;</span></h4>
	<h4>
		<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:verdana;">Force.com is the only proven enterprise platform for building and running business applications in the cloud. The Force.com platform powers the Salesforce CRM (<a href="http://www.salesforce.com/">http://www.salesforce.com/</a>) applications, more than 1,000 ISV partner applications like those from CA Technologies, FinancialForce.com and Fujitsu, and 200,000 custom applications used by salesforce.com&rsquo;s 92,300 customers such as Japan Post, Kaiser Permanente, KONE and Sprint Nextel. Force.com also enables developers to make any enterprise app social by leveraging the social collaboration components including profiles, status updates, and real-time feeds available with Chatter</span></h4>
</div>
 
	
